/**********************************************************************
*
*    README
*    ======
*
*    This README-file includes information about how to
*    build and run the Varkon PMdemo program.
*
*    (C)2007-01-18 J. Kjellander
*
***********************************************************************/

1. Make sure you have built the VU library (VUlib.a).
   See VU/src/README

2. cd to the PM/demo directory

3. A Makefile for linux is included in the demo directory.
   Type "make" to build the PM demo program.

4. Run the program.

/***********************************************************************/
